column5: Gents, Looknig to find out about camps or cabins for sale in the ontario area. any info would be great. Thanks

[font color=green size=3][b]My neighbor two cottages down put his up for sale,privately, in September, it's a pretty nice place, overlooking the lake. If you e-mail me I'll get you his phone number.I think he wants $225Cnd.
You could try the NOTO bulletin board - properties for sale seems to be the main discussion there. See http://www.noto.net/bulletins
Try norealtyfee.com - it is by city Good Luck - Rocfish
